messages.message: Hi Team I've had feedback that it's not very intuitive on how to start a new chat when you first open AI-Hub converse. I've sent a series of screenshots twice now showing how to navigate to and open a new chat to upload docs. Might be worth looking into how we can help guide the user on this in the platform.
P.S every time they ask they are embarrassed they couldn't work it out, so I'm sure more people just don't reach out :sweat_smile:
